{"tid":1329514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】張堅庭懇求林鄭鞠躬下台：每次加深大家嘅怨恨","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:40:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97ff893396f933d70bbc2ed332889d8c7305d9bb","tid":1329514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190718/59836864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59836864&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAygESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=ab4b8b20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59836864&h=8a83a142\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190718/59836864</a><br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】張堅庭懇求林鄭鞠躬下台：每次加深大家嘅怨恨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190718/large/1563435912_bace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190718%2Flarge%2F1563435912_bace.jpg&h=609670ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 攝影：陳俊強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「反送中」修例爭議持續數月，特首林鄭月娥近日與不同黨派的立法會議員會晤，已退休的資深傳媒人曾智華在社交平台狠批特首林鄭月娥「一人『有病』，全港蒙難」，竟因她一個人的決定，對抗全港幾百萬人的意願，導致香港民怨大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n張堅庭今日現身書展，為一本關於海外升學的新書舉行簽名會，講到近月香港有許多事發生，他認為林鄭責無旁貸：「香港&hellip;&hellip;我諗我覺得如果要對香港要負起一個歷史責任，林鄭月娥你真係要快啲用一個好合理嘅理由&hellip;&hellip;相信佢而家情緒比較焦慮，我諗佢瞓覺、睡眠都唔夠，同埋佢而家冇咗一個管治嘅意志，喺咁嘅情況，佢就盡量同中央商討，快啲畀佢落台，佢自己辭職，相信個社會起碼嗰個緊張變到從容，尤其市民同警察矛盾，你每一次都係加深大家嘅怨恨。」<br />\n<br />\n他有留意連月的警民衝突，持平地說：「搵唔到源頭，跟住你真係搵唔番個源頭，你又真係劈過我、我又揼過你，你話邊個唔啱？邊個都有唔啱嘅時侯，你再擺班人去最前方，呢個係一個好大嘅悲劇嚟，我諗喺最後關頭&hellip;&hellip;既然喺政治上犯咗啲錯誤，我覺得如果真係要為傷口補救，我覺得林鄭月娥係要負一個歷史責任，佢鞠躬下台我覺得對全世界都係一個最好嘅舉措，喺呢個懸崖嘅邊緣裏面，真係真係真係體現吓，鞠躬下台，起碼會有一個歷史嘅位置。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：張明<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【每周送10萬】<br />\n升級壹會員獨家尊享，立即參加10萬火急大抽獎 !<br />\n*推廣生意的競賽牌照號碼：52302-9<br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n錶迷必讀！<br />\n89頁腕時計電子書 66款嚴選年度新錶<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/e/v7jEA0MC1X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2Fe%2Fv7jEA0MC1X&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAygESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=a7ece4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/e/v7jEA0MC1X</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190718/large/1563436230_7294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190718%2Flarge%2F1563436230_7294.jpg&h=33a26799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張堅庭今日現身書展，為一本有關海外升學指南新書舉行簽書會。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190718/large/1563436230_6e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190718%2Flarge%2F1563436230_6e4d.jpg&h=0d8d31f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到近日香港各種事件，張堅庭指特首林鄭有歷史責任。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190718/large/1563436230_7ea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190718%2Flarge%2F1563436230_7ea6.jpg&h=e3c51ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張堅庭希望林鄭考慮辭職，平息事件。"},{"pid":"6749bf5540ee7eb278b9d51fbc4f15bcaddaf6c1","tid":1329514,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"下台咪又係另一件垃圾頂上，我哋係要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d19b6937dd3e12b152ab15dc04b3994820e092","tid":1329514,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}